# Incident Report: Windows Security Log Cleared

## Incident Summary

The Windows Security event log was cleared on the monitored endpoint. Clearing audit logs is commonly associated with defense evasion techniques used to remove forensic evidence.

---

## Incident Information

| Field | Value |
|--------|-------|
| Incident Name | Audit Log Cleared |
| Severity | High |
| Event ID | 1102 |
| Detection Source | Microsoft Sentinel |
| Data Source | Windows Security Logs |
| Affected Machine | SOC-WIN10-01 |
| Status | Investigated |

---

## Detection Logic

The analytics rule monitors Windows Security Event ID **1102**, which is generated whenever the Windows Security log is cleared.

